text: Karaguzhino () is a rural locality (a village) in Mindyaksky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 79 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 75 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Karaguzhino
